2. How We Retain and Transmit Your Personal Information
2.1 How we retain your personal information
We will retain your personal information for the minimum period needed to provide you with our products and/or services unless laws otherwise specify or unless you separately authorize us to retain the personal information for a longer period. After you take the initiative to request the deletion of your personal information in connection with the App or when the minimum retention period expires, we will delete or anonymize your personal information as soon as possible in accordance with laws and regulations, unless otherwise specified by laws and regulations. If laws specify a longer retention period, we will delete or anonymize the related personal information upon the expiration of this extended period.
We determine the minimum retention period mainly based on the following: (1) The purposes for which the personal information is processed: whether the purposes have been fulfilled or are unable to be fulfilled, or whether the processing becomes unnecessary due to business changes or discontinuance; (2) The amount, category, and sensitivity of the personal information; (3) The potential risks arising from unauthorized use or disclosure of your personal information; (4) The necessity to maintain relevant transaction and activity records to address your information query requests or complaints you might raise in the future; (5) The safeguards available to ensure the security and quality of the services we provide to you; (6) The data retention period otherwise specified by laws or administrative regulations.
If you have seriously violated laws, regulations, or our relevant product/service agreements, policies, or rules during your use of the App, the records of your violations as well as your credit records and personal information in relation to the App will be retained for the maximum period permitted by law.
If we discontinue the operations of some or all of our products or services for any special reason, we will inform you in advance and cease to collect and process your personal information in connection with the App. We will also delete or anonymize the personal information that we hold in connection with the discontinued products or services unless otherwise specified by laws and regulations.
