(I) We may access your clipboard to copy the coupon code or product description in Rewards to the clipboard so that you can quickly enter the relevant information when needed.
(J) We provide you with photo printing and derivative customization services. After you complete the payment to generate your order, we will store your order information, such as the store name, item specifications, payment amount, shipping fees, and the order completion time, and sync it with your account. For the purpose of fulfilling the contract, we will also collect the shipping address and the receiver's name and phone number that you submit.
The photo printing and derivative customization services will be provided by our partners. In order for them to produce and deliver the products that you order, we will share the above order and shipping information with them.
(K) We may use information about your device, such as the device name, device/phone model, IMEI number/OpenID, MAC address, serial number, IP address, and operating system version, and the phone number and email address linked to your account to provide you with push or notification services relating to HeyTap products or third-party content, including app updates and installations, sales and promotional messages, etc. You may opt out of receiving our sales and promotional messages by SMS or email, or by turning off the notification feature through "Settings - Notifications". Please note that the operation path may vary depending on the phone model or version.
(L) If you order a product or request a refund from us or use a paid service, we may collect your device identifiers (such as the IMEI number/OpenID), delivery details,
bank account number,
document type,
document number, phone number,
your name,
financial information (such as payment history and billing address)
, contact and communication records, etc. We will use such data to process your purchase orders and provide after-sales services, including customer support, order delivery, and invoice printing. If you do not provide this information, you may not be able to order a product, request a refund from us, or use a paid service.
(M) If you wish to participate in lucky draws or competitions, participate in promotional or marketing activities organized by us or our business partners, complete relevant surveys, or participate in user forums or blogs organized by us or our business partners, you may need to provide us with your name,
phone number, email address,
postal address,
bank account number
, and Alipay account number in order for us to contact you and send you rewards.
(N) When providing after-sales services and customer support to you, we may collect your location information to show you after-sales service centers nearby. We may request and collect your personal information, such as your device information (e.g., the IMEI number), your name,
phone number, email address,
postal address, and device logs, and we may
record
the calls between you and our customer service representatives. We use the data to diagnose product issues, repair customers' devices, and provide other customer care and support services. We may also collect your email address to respond to the questions raised or comments made by you in the "Contact Us" or "Data Subject Rights Platform" section of our website.
(O) In order to help us understand how you use our services, how you participate in promotional or marketing activities, user forums or blogs organized by us, or how you use after-sales services and customer support, we may use the phone number, email address, and other contact information you have provided to us in the aforementioned scenarios to conduct user research and follow-up surveys.
(P) In order to fulfill cybersecurity protection obligations, ensure the normal functioning of the HeyTap Product and the security of your account, and improve and optimize your user experience, we will collect the following information during your use of the HeyTap Product: information about your device such as the device name, device model, IMEI number, OpenID, MAC address, serial number, IP address, and operating system version, information about how you and your device interact with the HeyTap Product, information about operations performed by you after signing in to your HeyTap Account (
such as information about changing your password or the linked phone number or email address
and the manual account recovery history), the time and duration of your use of the HeyTap Product, the search keywords entered by you, and logs and information about events (such as restarts, upgrades, errors, and crashes). We collect such information to verify your identity, analyze the efficiency of our business operations, review transactions, and prevent fraud.
(Q)
We will use your personal information solely for the purposes described in this Privacy Notice. Your personal information will only be used for the purposes identified, described, and authorized by you at the time of collection. We will obtain your prior consent if we intend to use your personal information for any purposes other than those specified in this Privacy Notice. We will obtain your prior consent if we intend to use your personal information collected to fulfill a specific purpose for any other purpose. Without your consent, we will not provide your personal information or behavioral data to any third parties.
