The personal information collected by us will be retained for the minimum period needed to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected as described in this Privacy Notice, unless otherwise specified by applicable laws or regulations. We will completely delete or anonymize your personal information upon the expiration of the retention period or when it can be deleted.
If we stop some or all of our products or services for any special reason, we will promptly inform you and stop the collection and processing of your personal information in connection with such products or services, and delete or anonymize your personal information we hold that relates to the products or services, unless otherwise specified by laws and regulations.
4. How We Share, Transfer or Publicly Disclose Your Personal Information
4.1 How We Share and Transfer Your Personal Information
From time to time, we may share certain personal information with our affiliates and the strategic partners who work with us to provide products and services or otherwise share or transfer your personal information to provide the products or services requested by you.
(A)
Affiliates
: In order for us to provide services to you based on your HeyTap Account, we may share your personal information with our affiliates. For example, when you use the HeyTap Product with your HeyTap Account, we may share your personal information with our affiliates in order to assist you in accruing HeyTap Account reward points or obtaining user benefits such as redeeming your reward points or memberships when you use other products or features accessible from your HeyTap Account. We will only share necessary personal information.
If we or our affiliates intend to change the purpose for which your personal information is used and processed, we will obtain your authorization or consent again.
(B)
Sharing with our authorized partners
: Some of our services will be provided by our authorized partners only for the purposes stated in this Privacy Notice. We may share some of your personal information with our partners in order to provide services to you and improve your user experience. Specifically:
(1) We need to share your device information and behavioral data with our advertising and analytics service partners (including but not limited to advertising service providers, third-party ad monitoring service providers, and news feed service providers) in order to implement advertising and monitor the effectiveness of such advertising. We will share your personal information with such authorized partners only to the extent necessary.
(2) We may need to share your name, phone number, email address, postal address, bank account number, and Alipay account number with our marketing and promotional partners during events such as marketing and promotional activities that we entrust our partners to hold or that we hold jointly with the partners. With such information, the partners (third parties) can record your participation in the activities and send you rewards, including but not limited to sending entitlements or mailing rewards. For example, when we need to award you a prize for an activity, we will inform the logistics company of the contact information provided by you during the activity so as to complete the delivery of the prize to you.
(3) We may need to share your personal information with our service/content providers, including but not limited to cloud service providers, SMS or other technical service providers, payment or financial service providers, and short video content providers, so that they can provide you with the necessary product or service functions. For instance, when we entrust a third-party technical service provider to provide a speech-to-text conversion service, the service provider may receive and store some personal information, but they will not use such information for any other purposes.
(4) In certain circumstances, we will appoint a third party to process your personal information on our behalf. For example, companies that send SMS messages or emails or that provide technical support on our behalf are allowed to use your personal information only to provide you with the relevant services.
(C) In the event of a merger, acquisition, bankruptcy, or liquidation, if we need to transfer your personal information, we will request the new company or organization to which your personal information will be transferred to continue to be bound by this Privacy Notice; otherwise we will request such company or organization to obtain your authorization or consent again. If there is no need to transfer your personal information, we will fully inform you and delete or anonymize all personal information controlled by us.
We will share or transfer your personal information only for legitimate, proper, necessary, specific, and explicit purposes, and we will only share personal information which is necessary to provide a service. In addition, we will require the abovementioned third parties to take considerable confidentiality and security measures during their processing of your personal information by means of agreements or other appropriate measures.
