5. How We Protect Your Personal Information
5.1 How We Protect Your Personal Information
We adopt technical and organizational measures that are reasonable and actionable to protect the security of the information collected in connection with our services. We have introduced safeguards that satisfy industry standards to protect the personal information provided by you from unauthorized access, disclosure, use, or alteration, or from damage or loss. We will take all reasonable and actionable measures to protect your personal information. For example:
